sequenceDiagram
    participant Orch as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant BuiltIn as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP+mTLS
    participant LLMJudge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP+mTLS
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>HTTP

    Note over S3,HF: Flow 2: Model Initialization (startup)
    S3->>HF: KServe Storage Initializer<br/>downloads model files<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
    HF->>HF: Load model to /mnt/models<br/>Auto-detect architecture

    Note over Orch,BuiltIn: Flow 1: Built-in Detection (Regex/FileType/Custom)
    Orch->>BuiltIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP plaintext
    BuiltIn->>BuiltIn: Registry dispatch<br/>(regex, file_type, custom)
    BuiltIn-->>Orch: Detection results<br/>[{detection, detection_type, score}]

    Note over Orch,HF: Flow 2: HuggingFace ML Detection
    Orch->>HF: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP + mTLS (Istio)<br/>Auth: KServe
    HF->>HF: PyTorch inference<br/>AutoModelForSequenceClassification<br/>or GraniteForCausalLM
    HF-->>Orch: Classification results<br/>[{detection, detection_type, score}]

    Note over Orch,vLLM: Flow 3: LLM Judge Evaluation
    Orch->>LLMJudge: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP + mTLS (Istio)<br/>Auth: KServe
    LLMJudge->>vLLM: Evaluation prompt<br/>HTTP plaintext<br/>OpenAI-compatible API
    vLLM-->>LLMJudge: LLM evaluation result
    LLMJudge-->>Orch: Judge results<br/>[{detection, detection_type, score}]

    Note over Orch,LLMJudge: Flow 3b: LLM Judge Generation Evaluation
    Orch->>LLMJudge: POST /api/v1/text/generation<br/>HTTP + mTLS (Istio)
    LLMJudge->>vLLM: Prompt+generation pair<br/>evaluation request
    vLLM-->>LLMJudge: Evaluation result
    LLMJudge-->>Orch: Generation assessment<br/>[{detection, detection_type, score}]
